{"tid":1175420,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"vivo NEX 2 玩咁大？可拆卸鏡頭？","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T16:29:13.000Z","uid":159448,"like":10,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40ba3ad014118b9ffad8e8dee43574cb5f46fd8c","tid":1175420,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"近年智能電話的設計趨勢，除了出現摺疊式屏幕外，最多的便是追求全面屏幕。而 vivo 去年推出 NEX 時，以彈出式鏡頭設計造就了「真。全面屏幕」的效果，跟當時瀏海屏幕及水滴屏幕那些非真正全面屏幕作出了巨大對比。<br />\n<br />\n而作為全面屏幕的領先者，隨著 Asus 的 Zenfone 6 出現的翻轉式鏡頭出現而受到了一定程度的挑戰，而一年過後又是下一代 NEX 準備出現的時候，vivo 會有甚麼利器呢？Vivo 近日展示的 APEX (2019) 概念設計圖，也是跟 NEX 一樣採用全面屏幕設計，而這並非開孔式屏幕，莫非也是繼續採用彈出式鏡頭呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前有消息指，vivo 或在下一代 NEX：NEX 2 在鏡頭方面作出一個令人驚訝的鏡頭設計 &ndash; 採用可拆卸模組式後置鏡頭！而洩露這個消息的人士暗示洩密管道相當可靠。<br />\n<br />\n而從插圖來看，該可拆卸的鏡頭模組置於機背的主鏡頭位置，用戶只要把鏡頭模組取下 (估計以磁力方式連接)，便可以把相信作前置鏡頭，甚至可以說是一個可移動鏡頭！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個方案的好處，除了可以削走前置鏡頭，跟 Zenfone 6 一樣以主鏡頭取代了前置鏡頭的功能外，而且用戶同樣能把擺放在一些比較難拍攝的位置取景等。但是缺點就是該鏡頭是以模組方式設計，供電方面要依靠內置電池，但是電池的容量會因鏡頭模組尺寸所影響，所以可能拍幾張照片便會充電。<br />\n<br />\n不過最終是否採納這個方案還是有待進一步的消息了。。。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2VaNmv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2VaNmv.png&h=bf468a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBxsPzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBxsPzQ.jpg&h=e54f241f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irUnDtb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirUnDtb.jpg&h=a3370f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGuF9zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGuF9zR.jpg&h=afd647d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"3321a5c3faaa0ae27dc1e96b814966cac637d515","tid":1175420,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"依家智能電話最大敵人就係前置鏡頭，點解唔直接取佢？咁咪可以完全解決問題囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1152904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1152904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a0f9239f542ac85c944c67aff1ed5cbc881e63c","tid":1175420,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"我部dream phone終於推出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過可惜係支那機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cf060696e61c0c8cbc99e35186727e60fecad9","tid":1175420,"uid":80179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"華為衰落 vivo成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19731317b7becb66f0df6793ae9e138892a22043","tid":1175420,"uid":13010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"偷拍用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c8b1cae4d3d3db6d9d7d3a003f198ab0015e62","tid":1175420,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b48458f8d8ec1ced1ae3f73418371c4fa9c2e234","tid":1175420,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3321a5c3faaa0ae27dc1e96b814966cac637d515","tid":1175420,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"依家智能電話最大敵人就係前置鏡頭，點解唔直接取佢？咁咪可以完全解決問題囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1152904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1152904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"巴打有遠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea69b0f6541704ff5d05f93f2f6a95333b789f2","tid":1175420,"uid":133086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:49:23.000Z","msg":"一定好易唔見 到時賣返1000蚊粒 fat fat la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aed23f44b2263c36f226b326bd9a8ffa7c149e9"